        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
          <p>This is a web application that will generate a random quote and allow the user to post to Twitter using the provided button. The layout was constructed with HTML5, CSS3, Sass and Bootstrap (version 4). The functionality is provided by jQuery and an API. The user can click on the Twitter button to compose a tweet with the provided quote (and quote author). Clicking the 'New Quote' button will generate a new random quote.</p>
          <p>Visit the application here: <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" href="https://codepen.io/nlanky/full/ZrMeYw">codepen.io/nlanky/full/ZrMeYw</a></p>
